data.description: This beautifully updated home offers a perfect blend of character & modern amenities. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood w/no HOA, this property provides a peaceful retreat. The spacious yard is fully fenced, ensuring privacy & a secure space for outdoor activities. Inside, you'll find a host of upgrades, incl updated bathrooms & luxury vinyl planking throughout, adding a touch of elegance to the living spaces. The kitchen boasts granite countertops & painted cabinets, creating a stylish & functional cooking space. The addition of SS appliances enhances the overall modern feel. Enjoy cozy evenings by the fireplace in the family room, making it a perfect spot to unwind. The brand new chimney adds both functionality & aesthetic appeal. An upstairs loft addition provides additional space, ideal for a home office or recreational area. Practical features such as a water softener & water purification system contribute to the overall comfort of the home. Outside, a mini barn in the backyard adds extra storage space & versatility. This home is not just a place to live; it's a haven of comfort & style, ready to welcome its new owners. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own.
